high_descs: Move to the counter near the coffee machine.
Pick up the knife that is right of the coffee machine.
Turn left, move to the island where the apple is.
Cut the apple into sections.
Turn right, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Place the knife in to the refrigerator.
Turn left, move to the island where the apple is.
Pick up a section of apple.
Turn right, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Place the apple section into the refrigerator, chill it, pick it up again.
Turn right, move to in front of the stove.
Place the apple section into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Section an apple, chill one of the sections.

high_descs: Turn right, then left and head towards the counter in front of you.
Take the knife by the coffee machine on the counter in front of you.
Turn around then face the green island on your right.
Slice the apple on the island in front of you.
Turn right, then left, then face the fridge on your right.
Open the fridge, place the knife inside and close the fridge.
Turn right, then right again and face the island on your right.
Take an apple slice from the island in front of you.
Turn right, then left and face the fridge on your right.
Place the apple slice inside of the fridge, take it out and close the fridge.
Turn right, then head towards the microwave on top of the stove.
Place the apple slice in the microwave on top of the stove and close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold apple slice in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the wall and then turn left and walk across the room.
pick up the knife on the edge of the counter.
Turn around and walk halfway across the room and then turn right to face the kitchen table.
Cut the apple in half.
Turn right and take a step, then turn left and walk across the room then turn right to face the cabinet.
Open the cabnet and place the knife on the shelf.
Turn to the right, then walk across the room, then turn right and walk halfway across the room, and then turn right to face the table.
Pick up half of the apple.
Turn right and take a step, then turn left and walk across the room then turn right to face the cabinet.
Open the cabinet, place the apple inside, then close the cabinet, then open the cabinet and remove the apple half.
Turn right, walk across the room, then turn right and walk halfway across the room, then turn right and face the table.
Turn to the right and walk across the room to face the stove and place the apple on a pan.
anns.task_desc: To cut an apple in half, as well as put half of it on the stove.

high_descs: Walk around the right side of the table and face the counter with the coffee maker on it.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk forward and then turn right to face the table with a tomato on it.
Cut the apple into three pieces.
Walk around the table and turn right to face the fridge.
Place the knife on the top shelf in the fridge.
Turn right and walk around the room and face the side of the table with the apple pieces on it.
Pick up a piece of the apple on the table.
Walk to the right of the table and turn right to face the fridge.
Cool the apple piece in the fridge and then remove it.
Turn right and walk forward to face the microwave.
Put the piece of apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: cut plus cool a piece of apple as well as place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk around the right side of the center table and walk forward to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk forward until beside the table, then turn right to face the table.
Cut the apple on the table into 3 pieces.
Walk around the right side of the table and face the fridge on the right.
Place the knife on the top shelf in the fridge.
Turn right and walk around to the end of the table with the apple on it.
Pick up a piece of apple from on the table.
Walk around the right side of the table and face the fridge on the right.
Cool the piece of apple in the fridge and then remove it.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Put the piece of apple into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cut plus cool a piece of apple as well as store it in the microwave.
